#:kivy 1.11.1

Sizing and positioning part 3
#:kivy 1.11.1

<FunkyButton>:
    canvas:
        Rectangle:
            pos: self.x + 50, self.y + 50
            size: 100, 100

    Button:
        pos: root.x + 50, root.y + 50
        size_hint: None, None
        size: 200, 200
        background_color: 1, 0, 0, 1

Sizing and positioning part 4
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height
        
        Button:
            text: 'Button 1'
            pos_hint: {'x': .1, 'y': .1}
            size_hint: .8, .1

        Button:
            text: 'Button 2'
            pos_hint: {'x': .1, 'y': .6}
            size_hint: .8, .1

Sizing and positioning elements part 5
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height

        GridLayout:
            cols: 2
            pos_hint: {'x': .3, 'y': .3}
            size_hint: None, None
            size: root.width * .4, root.width * .4

            Button:
                text: 'Button 1'
            Button:
                text: 'Button 2'
            Button:
                text: 'Button 3'
            Button: 
                text: 'Button 4'

Displaying text
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height

        Label:
            text: 'Here is some text in a label'
            pos_hint: {'x': .1, 'y': .8}
            size_hint: .8, .1
            halign: 'left'
            text_size: self.size
            font_size: 50
            bold: True
            color: 0, 1, 0, 1

Displaying images
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:
    canvas:
        BorderImage:
            source: 'images/bote.png'
            pos: 300, 300
            size: 300, 300

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height

        Image:
            source: 'images/bote.png'
            pos_hint: {'x': .25, 'y': .25}
            size_hint: .5, .5

Properties
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height

        Label:
            text: "I have " + str(root.numeric) + " chickens."

Buttons
#:kivy 1.11.1

<GameScreen>:

    FloatLayout:
        pos: 0, 0
        size: root.width, root.height

        Button:
            text: 'Press me'
            on_press: root.press_button()